type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Absolutely. The trail around Bass Lake is a scenic, mulch-surfaced loop that is perfect for dogs. It connects to the paved greenway system as well.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Are unleashed dogs allowed in Holly Springs?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"No, Holly Springs requires all dogs to be on a leash when not in a designated dog park or on private property. This ensures the safety of all trail users.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Is the Farmers Market dog-friendly?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes, the Holly Springs Farmers Market is a very pet-friendly event. It’s a great place to socialize your dog while shopping for local goods.\"}}]}4:[\"$\",\"script\",null,{\"type\":\"application/ld+json\",\"suppressHydrationWarning\":true,\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"$d\"}}]\n5:[\"$\",\"script\",null,{\"type\":\"application/ld+json\",\"suppressHydrationWarning\":true,\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"{\\\"@context\\\":\\\"https://schema.org\\\",\\\"@type\\\":\\\"BreadcrumbList\\\",\\\"itemListElement\\\":[{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ListItem\\\",\\\"position\\\":1,\\\"name\\\":\\\"Home\\\",\\\"item\\\":\\\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\\\"},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ListItem\\\",\\\"position\\\":2,\\\"name\\\":\\\"Dog Parks Directory\\\",\\\"item\\\":\\\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\\\"},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ListItem\\\",\\\"position\\\":3,\\\"name\\\":\\\"Holly Springs\\\"}]}\"}}]\n6:[\"$\",\"$Le\",null,{\"variant\":\"light\"}]\n7:[\"$\",\"$Lf\",null,{\"items\":[{\"id\":\"city-hero\",\"title\":\"City Overview\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"city-insights\",\"title\":\"Quick Facts\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"city-comparison\",\"title\":\"Top Comparisons\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"park-collections\",\"title\":\"Park Collections\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"neighborhood-clusters\",\"title\":\"Neighborhoods\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"park-types-guide\",\"title\":\"Park Type Guide\",\"level\":1