\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"chip-label\",\"children\":\"Dog Parks\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"chip-value\",\"children\":\"1\"}],\"$undefined\"]}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-description\",\"children\":\"Rated as one of the safest towns in NC, Holly Springs is an idyllic place for pets. From the open fields of Sugg Farm to the waterside trails of Bass Lake, it is pure suburban bliss.\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"city-rich-description\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",\"0\",{\"className\":\"rich-description-paragraph\",\"children\":[\"Holly Springs, North Carolina, has rapidly evolved from a quiet crossroads into a premier suburban destination, and its amenities for families and pets have led the way. The town’s approach to recreation is centered on \",[\"$\",\"$L11\",\"1\",{\"href\":\"https://www.hollyspringsnc.gov/321/Sugg-Farm-at-Bass-Lake-Park\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"rich-link\",\"children\":\"Sugg Farm Park\"}],null,\", a sprawling venue that hosts festival events and serves as the home for the community dog park. This off-leash area is beloved for its open, grassy space where dogs can romp freely in a safe, fenced environment. It is a true community gathering spot where neighbors catch up while their dogs play.\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"1\",{\"className\":\"rich-description-paragraph\",\"children\":[\"Bass Lake Park offers a different but equally appealing experience. The mulch-covered loop trail around the lake is a favorite for runners and dog walkers alike, offering a soft surface that is easy on the joints and paws. The trail is shaded and scenic, providing a daily dose of nature that feels far removed from the hustle of the Triangle. With a strong commitment to safety and cleanliness, Holly Springs expects owners to be responsible, but in return, it offers some of the most pleasant and well-maintained public spaces in the region. Whether browsing the dog-friendly Farmers Market or hitting the trails, it is a \",[\"$\",\"$L11\",\"1\",{\"href\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"rich-link\",\"children\":\"wonderful place to be a dog\"}],null,\".\"]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-cta-row\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L10\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-cta primary\",\"targetId\":\"park-directory\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-list-check\"}],\"Browse directory\"]}],[\"$\",\"$L10\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-cta ghost\",\"targetId\":\"map-and-neighborhoods\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-geo-alt\"}],\"Open map\"]}],[\"$\",\"$L11\",null,{\"href\":\"/list-your-park\",\"className\":\"hero-cta text-link\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-plus-circle\"}],\"Submit a park\"]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-footnotes\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",\"Sugg Farm Dog Park\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-sparkles\"}],\" \",\"Sugg Farm Dog Park\"]}],[\"$\",\"span\",\"Bass Lake Loop\",{\"children\":[\"$L12\",\" \",\"Bass Lake Loop\"]}],\"$L13\"]}]]}],\"$L14\"]}]}],\"$L15\",\"$L16\",\"$L17\",\"$L18\",\"$L19\",\"$L1a\",\"$undefined\",\"$L1b\",\"$L1c\",\"$L1d\",\"$L1e\",\"$L1f\"]}]\n9:[\"$\",\"footer\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-new\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-container\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-grid\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-column\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h4\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-heading\",\"children\":\"IndoorDogPark\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-links\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L11\",null,{\"href\":\"/about\",\"children\":\"About us\"}]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L11\",null,{\"href\":\"/partners\",\"children\":\"Partners\"}]}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-column\",\"childr